  "lyrics": "Wide open, I am wide open, I am wide open for you As I am crawling for you I'm open wide, I'm open wide, I'm open wide for you Show me what you wanna do Oh, my halfway home The time to get up, the time to get real Where do you know it? Do you show? The space between your eyes, oh baby, you Lost another time Phenomenic on the brim Oh, you're phenomenic to pride Oh, sorry you got to let go Baby, no, you are me The creator of the divine me Oh, drop it like a different noise Oh, it's time for me to say goodnight Thanks for watching! Thanks for watching! Thanks for watching! Thanks for watching!",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 15.380000114440918,
      "text": "Wide open, I am wide open, I am wide open for you",
      "start": 3.240000009536743
    },
    {
      "end": 22.3799991607666,
      "text": "As I am crawling for you",
      "start": 17.440000534057617
    },
    {
      "end": 32.380001068115234,
      "text": "I'm open wide, I'm open wide, I'm open wide for you",
      "start": 24.100000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 39.380001068115234,
      "text": "Show me what you wanna do",
      "start": 35.599998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 48.13999938964844,
      "text": "Oh, my halfway home",
      "start": 39.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 53.52000045776367,
      "text": "The time to get up, the time to get real",
      "start": 49.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 58.79999923706055,
      "text": "Where do you know it?",
      "start": 53.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 62.7400016784668,
      "text": "Do you show?",
      "start": 59.20000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 72.44000244140625,
      "text": "The space between your eyes, oh baby, you",
      "start": 65.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 77.73999786376953,
      "text": "Lost another time",
      "start": 73.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 82.54000091552734,
      "text": "Phenomenic on the brim",
      "start": 78.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 90.58000183105469,
      "text": "Oh, you're phenomenic to pride",
      "start": 83.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 102.33999633789062,
      "text": "Oh, sorry you got to let go",
      "start": 95.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 109.95999908447266,
      "text": "Baby, no, you are me",
      "start": 103.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 118.36000061035156,
      "text": "The creator of the divine me",
      "start": 110.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 127.5999984741211,
      "text": "Oh, drop it like a different noise",
      "start": 118.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 133.4199981689453,
      "text": "Oh, it's time for me to say goodnight",
      "start": 128.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 178.32000732421875,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!",
